description: Do you ever want to listen to swiggity swooty? Well, this skill plays 90 seconds of the clip on your Echo! Just ask Alexa and she'll obey!
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask your boy about swiggity swooty coming for that booty
Alexa, tell your boy about swiggity swooty
Alexa, ask your boy about that booty
name: Swiggity Swooty
